{
  "subject": "Mentorship completed \u2014 got 60 seconds for a review?",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Mentorship completed</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EDEBE4;\">\n<div style=\"display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;\">{{mentor_name}} marked your mentorship as completed \u2014 leave a review</div>\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#EDEBE4\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 12px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:600px;max-width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #DEDBD1;\">\n<tr><td bgcolor=\"#CDE8C6\" style=\"padding:28px 40px;border-radius:14px 14px 0 0;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://openmentor.io/brand/logo/png/icon-app/icon-app-128.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" alt=\"OpenMentor\" style=\"display:block;margin:0 auto;border:0;\"><div style=\"padding-top:16px;font:bold 24px/1.2 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#161A20;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:-0.5px;\">Mentorship completed</div></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 40px 0;\" align=\"center\"><div style=\"font:normal 15px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#5B6270;\">{{mentor_name}} marked your mentorship as completed. We hope it moved the needle, {{first_name}}.</div><div style=\"padding-top:14px;font:normal 15px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#161A20;\"><b>Got 60 seconds?</b> A review helps the next mentee decide \u2014 and it's the only &quot;payment&quot; free mentors ever get.</div><div style=\"padding-top:10px;font:normal 22px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#17C3B2;letter-spacing:4px;\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:18px 40px 0;\" align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#132A52\" style=\"border-radius:12px;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://openmentor.io/reviews/new?request_id={{request_id}}\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:15px 32px;font:bold 15px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;\">Leave a review for {{mentor_name}}</a></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:26px 40px 28px;\" align=\"center\"><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #DEDBD1;padding-top:16px;font:normal 11px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#5B6270;\">openmentor.io \u00b7 reviews are public, your email never is</div></td></tr>\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>",
  "text": "Hi {{first_name}},\n\n{{mentor_name}} marked your mentorship as completed. We hope it moved the needle!\n\nGot 60 seconds? A review helps the next mentee decide \u2014 and it's the only \"payment\" free mentors ever get.\n\nLeave a review for {{mentor_name}}:\nhttps://openmentor.io/reviews/new?request_id={{request_id}}\n\nReviews are public, your email never is.\n\n---\nopenmentor.io \u00b7 free mentorship for the tech community\nhttps://openmentor.io"
}
